        "y2": 521.519775390625
      },
      "layout_tag": "paragraph",
      "confidence": 0.9212076663970947,
      "reading_order": 4,
      "text": "other animals such as cow and goat\n(primary consumers) as food and\nare thus called the secondary\nconsumers.\nHow are decomposers useful to us?"
